format": "dash-1645685959915332v - 720x1280 (DASH video)"}, {"format_id": "dash-2547825988952434v", "ext": "mp4", "width": 1080, "height": 1920, "tbr": 1215.799, "format_note": "DASH video", "container": "mp4_dash", "vcodec": "vp09.00.40.08.00.01.01.01.00", "acodec": "none", "dynamic_range": "SDR", "url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t2/f2/m367/AQP_IISxuvu1JNiskMmHgI1wxjPLE_7I4OiVS7NLBWqONhmkoGcs6wEAzreuQSeWk7IpkCe88Ae-0gPscMQGZW-WZjf7syGcSAbx708.mp4?_nc_cat=110&_nc_sid=9ca052&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_ohc=zb26HJB2ZxAQ7kNvwFAwHQq&%3D&ccb=17-1&_nc_gid=_WL9e9sh1K0YrOCdVysviA&_nc_zt=28&_nc_ss=7a32e&oh=00_Af2H5Yj-xmnm8Tq_6vEJleDtGRWLABrWbAoSEOd-clt4Bw&oe=69D4CDE7", "manifest_stream_number": 0, "is_dash_periods": true, "protocol": "https", "video_ext": "mp4", "audio_ext": "none", "abr": 0, "vbr": 1215.799, "resolution": "1080x1920", "aspect_ratio": 0.56, "filesize_approx": 8112418, "http_headers": {"User-Agent": "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/143.0.0.0 Safari/537.36", "Accept": "text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8", "Accept-Language": "en-us,en;q=0.5", "Sec-Fetch-Mode": "navigate", "Referer": "https://www.instagram.com/"}, "format": "dash-2547825988952434v - 1080x1920 (DASH video)"}], "title": "Video by joshuaspoetry", "description": "What do you think about this?", "duration": 53.38, "timestamp": 1769561503, "uploader_id": "65324209519", "uploader": "Joshua De Schutter", "channel": "joshuaspoetry", "like_count": 119877, "comment_count": 2287, "comments": [{"author": "mekitty1", "author_id": "242614749", "id": "18339893248246635", "text": "Hard truth.  I ha", "timestamp": 1775104577}, {"author": "amandarosestudios", "author_id": "1941973586", "id": "18342628693245681", "text": "The only point of reference a parent has is what they didn’t get as a child, what hurt them as a child. There is a saying that says ‘Parenthood comes with no manual’, but it’s more complicated than that. And most of us were still raising ourselves when the babies started coming. Give good parents a little grace.", "timestamp": 1775098729}, {"author": "homaniroomand", "author_id": "4201981690", "id": "18073596620639913", "text": "👏👏👏👏👏👏👏", "timestamp": 1775093071}, {"author": "eliana_abigailluh", "author_id": "48032826914", "id": "18070898900655591", "text": "And what they missed was parents who stayed together (yes, on both sides) so they stayed together \"for the kids\"", "timestamp": 1775080757}, {"author": "pogo.g12", "author_id": "51653431836", "id": "18577906513002019", "text": "Break the curses your parents couldn’t", "timestamp": 1775079409}, {"author": "hazel_luvvs", "author_id": "76650206323", "id": "18355449280238690", "text": "I understand it’s their first time at life but it’s also my first time too…", "timestamp": 1775069572}, {"author": "mohammad_kamal2028", "author_id": "49574938624", "id": "18120769711625639", "text": "This is what my parents tried to do to me they tried to force me to be a doctor because my dad never got the chance to be a doctor they bragged about how they made all the mistakes with me so they didn’t make them with my younger brother as if I was a mistake which I always was to my parents and they don’t care about what I needed otherwise they would let me be myself but they never did", "timestamp": 1774997509}, {"author": "somewherecanyon", "author_id": "807135396", "id": "18455237413107044", "text": "Good parents understand their kids 🔥", "timestamp": 1774990350}, {"author": "_cali.finesse710", "author_id": "67503141514", "id": "18147466321473703", "text": "👏👏👏👏", "timestamp": 1774987834}], "thumbnails": [{"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/623483768_923866353397899_5542140922165326644_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDB4MTEzNi5zZHIuZjcxODc4LmRlZmF1bHRfY292ZXJfZnJhbWUuYzIifQ&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=103&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2